  <lyrics>[V1]
 Munakuwan Jesusniy, Palabrampi Pay niwan.
 Wawas riyta atinku munakoj Salvadorman.
 
[C]
 //Dios munakuwan.//
 Bibliapi Pay niwan.
 
[V2]
 Cristo cruzpi wañorqa, glorianman kicharerqa.
 Juchasniyta Pay qhechun, cielonman pusawanqa.
 
[V3]
 Munakuwan Jesusniy, chaymanta kusikuni.
 Jesús k'acha Michejniy waqaychaspa pusawan.
 
[V4]
 Pisi kallpa kajtiypis Jesusniy kallpachawan.
 Cielonman pusawajtin, wiñay kusiypi kasaj.</lyrics></song>